Insider Activity


Individual




April Hoxie Foley



Ms. April H. Foley is Independent Class II Director at Vista Outdoor, Inc. and Independent Director at Xerium Technologies, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Vista Outdoor, Inc., Xerium Technologies, Inc., Center for Advanced Defense Studies, Council for A Community of Democracies and Smith College. Ms. Foley was previously employed as Independent Director by Alliant Techsystems, Inc., Vice Chairman & Vice President by Export-Import Bank of the United States, and Director-Business Planning by PepsiCo, Inc. She received her undergraduate degree from Smith College and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



