April Hoxie Foley, MBA

Age : 68Public asset : 687,329 USDLinked companies :  Vista Outdoor Inc -  Xerium Technologies, Inc. 





Summary 



Ms. April H. Foley is on the Board of Directors at Vista Outdoor, Inc., Xerium Technologies, Inc., Center for Advanced Defense Studies, Council for A Community of Democracies and Smith College. Ms. Foley was previously employed as an Independent Director by Alliant Techsystems, Inc., Vice Chairman & Vice President by Export-Import Bank of the United States, and Director-Business Planning by PepsiCo, Inc.She received her undergraduate degree from Smith College and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



